num::<impl u16>::to_be.doc:
Converts `self` to big endian from the target's endianness.

On big endian this is a no-op. On little endian the bytes are
swapped.

# Examples

```

if cfg!(target_endian = "big") {
    assert_eq!(n.to_be(), n)
} else {
    assert_eq!(n.to_be(), n.swap_bytes())
}
```

